OL,3,CChristmas attractions face sharp rise
OL,4,Cin property taxes after Budget
OL,6,FLondon's Winter Wonderland and Hamleys
OL,7,Fare set to be hit by sharp jumps in
OL,8,Ftheir property taxes from next year as
OL,9,FUK Christmas attractions come under
OL,10,Fpressure from next year's business
OL,11,Frates overhaul.
OL,13,FAnalysis of official figures has shown
OL,14,Fthat a raft of Christmas attractions,
OL,15,Fmarkets and destination-led retail
OL,16,Fwill face increases in business rates
OL,17,Fpayments from April.
