OL,3,CChristmas attractions face sharp rise
OL,4,Cin property taxes after Budget
OL,6,FHowever, other major retail
OL,7,Fdestinations and Christmas shopping
OL,8,Flocations, such as Harrods, will see
OL,9,Ftheir payments fall due to new
OL,10,Fproperty valuations.
OL,12,FIn last month's Budget, the Chancellor
OL,13,Fannounced a current 40% discount for
OL,14,Fretail, hospitality and leisure
OL,15,Fbusinesses ` which is capped at
OL,16,F#110,000 per business ` will end on
OL,17,FMarch 31 next year.
