OL,3,CChristmas attractions face sharp rise
OL,4,Cin property taxes after Budget
OL,6,FThis will be replaced by a new system
OL,7,Ffrom the next financial year, which
OL,8,Fwill see rates multipliers for retail,
OL,9,Fhospitality and leisure firms set 5p
OL,10,Flower than the standard rate with no
OL,11,Fcap in support.
OL,13,FThe Government also launched a #3.2
OL,14,Fbillion scheme of transitional relief
OL,15,Fto cap annual rises.
OL,17,FHowever, new property valuations will
OL,18,Fbe used to decide rate payments from
OL,19,FApril, with many of these updates
OL,20,Fleading to significant increases.
