OL,3,CChristmas attractions face sharp rise
OL,4,Cin property taxes after Budget
OL,6,FCalculations of Valuation Office
OL,7,FAgency (VOA) data by global tax firm
OL,8,FRyan found that the land used for
OL,9,FWinter Wonderland in Hyde Park sees
OL,10,Fits rateable value (RV) jump from
OL,11,F#1.0m to #3.75m, up 275%, pushing its
OL,12,Fbill from #555,000 to #721,500 next
OL,13,Fyear, despite a cap.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Lapland UK in Ascot see its
OL,16,Frateable value surge from #150,000 to
OL,17,F#1.87 million.
