OL,6,FOther major visitor destinations are
OL,7,Falso set to be affected, Camden
OL,8,FStables Market's annual bill is set to
OL,9,Frise from #699,300 to #909,090 next
OL,10,FApril after its valuation jumped by
OL,11,F178%.
OL,13,FHamleys' flagship toy store on Regent
OL,14,FStreet, London, will face one of the
OL,15,Flargest bill increases, rising by
OL,16,F#449,550 next April.
