OL,3,CChristmas attractions face sharp rise
OL,4,Cin property taxes after Budget
OL,6,FHowever, other retailers will see
OL,7,Ftheir payments fall, with Waterstones'
OL,8,Fflagship store in Piccadilly, London,
OL,9,Fset to see its bill fall by 45%,
OL,10,Faround #828,000, from next year.
OL,12,FAlex Probyn, practice leader for
OL,13,FEurope and Asia-Pacific property tax
OL,14,Fat Ryan, told the Press Association:
OL,15,F"Seasonal attractions have grown
OL,16,Fsignificantly in popularity between
OL,17,Fvaluation dates, so upward pressure on
OL,18,Ftheir valuations was not unexpected
OL,19,Fbut the level of increases were.
