OL,6,F"The key question is whether the
OL,7,Ffigures reflect their short seasonal
OL,8,Frental model or whether broader income
OL,9,Findicators have influenced the
OL,10,Foutcome. For temporary attractions,
OL,11,Fgetting that balance right is critical.
OL,13,F"Across the wider retail sector, we're
OL,14,Fseeing extremes both geographically
OL,15,Fand by format."
